Package com.colorfulsoftware.rss Description

RSSpect v1.0.2 - a Java feed library for the RSS 2.0 specification.

Use this library to add rss feeds into your application. The api is driven by the RSSDoc class which enables you to read and write rss documents. The RSS element and all of its sub elements are serializable, immutable and thread safe. See the Project Page for examples of how to use the API.
